title: Acer Nitro V Gaming Laptop | AMD Ryzen 7 8845HS Octa-Core AI Capable Processor | NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4060 Laptop GPU | 16" WUXGA IPS 165Hz Display | 16GB DDR5 | 1TB Gen 4 SSD | Wi-Fi 6E | ANV16-41-R5J0
description:
About this item    Revolutionizing Performance: The AMD Ryzen 7 8845HS processor is crafted to provide outstanding premium experiences. Immerse yourself in high-speed performance while streaming and gaming, relishing reliable functionality, intelligent battery management, and groundbreaking technologies that bring the AI experience closer to you.    AI-Driven Graphics: Experience lifelike visuals and unparalleled performance with the cutting-edge NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4060 laptop graphics. The integration of DLSS 3.5 technology takes your gaming to new heights, enhancing beauty, immersion, and realism. This innovative AI-powered technique elevates the quality of ray tracing, providing an even more captivating gaming experience.    Picture-Perfect. Furiously Fast: Engage thoroughly with a captivating 16-inch 165Hz display that comes to life featuring a 16:10 WUXGA 1920 x 1200 resolution. The brilliance of vibrant sRGB 100% ensures that each color maintains its pristine quality. The Mux Switch offers a visual spectacle where each frame remains flawless, and every movement is free from tearing.    Internal Specifications: 16GB DDR5 Memory (2 DDR5 Slots Total, Maximum 32GB); 1TB PCIe Gen 4 SSD (2 x PCIe M.2 Slots) | Ports For All Your Accessories: 1 - USB Type-C Port- - supporting USB4 (up to 40 Gbps), DisplayPort over USB Type-C, & USB Charging, 2 - USB 3.2 Gen 2 Ports (One Featuring Power-off Charging), 1 - HDMI 2.1 Port with HDCP support, 1 - Headphone/Speaker/Line-out Jack, 1 - Ethernet (RJ-45), DC-in for AC adapter, 1 - Kensington Lock Slot    Copilot in Windows: Introducing Copilot in Windows (in preview) a new AI-powered intelligent assistant designed to provide answers and inspirations from the web, foster creativity and collaboration, and assist in maintaining focus on your tasks. Activating Copilot is easy; simply use the dedicated Copilot key on the keyboard.    Stay Connected: Your gaming sanctuary is wherever you are. On the couch? Settle in with fast and stable Wi-Fi 6E. Gaming Cafe? Get an edge online with Gigabit Ethernet. No matter your location, Nitro V 16 ensures you're always in the driver's seat.    Cooling Mastery: The Nitro V 16 enhances cooling with a dual-fan quad-intake and quad-exhaust system. The system draws cold air from the top keyboard and button cover and expels heat through side and rear vents, eliminating throttling and ensuring peak CPU and GPU performance.    
   AI-Powered Gaming Communication: Elevate your gaming and streaming experience with Purified Voice 2.0, coupled with a three-microphone design. This advanced feature utilizes AI to eliminate ambient noises, ensuring that your voice commands remain at the forefront, providing clear communication during intense gaming sessions. No Limits with NitroSense: Channel your inner gaming strategist with the NitroSense utility app. Fine-tune your gaming setup to match your style, be it adjusting fan speeds for those heated battles or customizing lighting for immersive exploration. The power is at your fingertips, transforming your laptop into a perfectly calibrated command center for every gaming mission.   Show more     See more product details
